<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴斯家的孩子们到家时，天已经开始黑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想长大了。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的嘴唇颤抖着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“长大不是问题。”潘瑟温柔地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“问题是我们长得太快了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们还没准备好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。我觉得这里的人就是很刻薄。”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在芝加哥，没人会说那么让人讨厌的话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是你不知道而已，鲍比。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我知道。这个镇上的人都很刻薄，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且这里太无聊了！”鲍比继续说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果没有休伊的话，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们在这里根本没事情可做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们同意了鲍比的说法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得今天的愿望对我们来说是个很好的教训。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“至少我们知道了我们长大以后会是什么样子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊大笑着拍拍自己的肚子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，孩子们出现了和早上一样四肢发痒的感觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的胳膊和腿变短了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊的肚子消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比的小胖肚子却又长出来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几分钟后，他们又恢复了孩子的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“重新回到孩子的样子真好。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们互相拥抱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们进去吃点东西吧。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吃晚饭的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨告诉了孩子们她今天做的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我带着兰姆去了公园。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们看到了几个大人在公园里到处跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的行为就像孩子一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许他们只是想玩儿玩儿。”赛伊轻声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玩儿玩儿没关系，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但人们的举止应该和他们的年纪相符！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们看了看彼此。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我同意玛莎阿姨的说法。”简说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的举止应该与我们的年龄相符。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，孩子们做好了外出的准备。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨带着兰姆去了花园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天轮到你了，鲍比。”赛伊耳语道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没有愿望啊。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能明天再许愿吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他孩子想了想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，潘瑟说：“我们每人都可以跳过一次。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们今天不去见休伊了。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟读了一本书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简玩儿玩具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊去骑车了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比什么都没干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不想出去，也不喜欢读书，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>更不想玩儿玩具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里太无聊了。”他一直嘟囔着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你为什么不找点事情做呢？”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里没事情可做啊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个镇子太无聊了！”他抱怨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想念芝加哥。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里总是有很多好玩的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比，我们最近有过很多次探险了。”潘瑟说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还觉得无聊吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望这里发生点有意思的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在这儿，在镇子上。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟转了转眼珠，然后又埋头去读书了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，鲍比坐了起来打了个响指。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对了！”他叫道，“我知道我要许什么愿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，鲍比的心情好多了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨天没许愿挺好的。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，我终于读完我的书了。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不用去担心恐龙的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也不用管那些刻薄的人。”简咯咯笑道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，我今天准备好许愿了。”鲍比激动地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为某些原因，其他人并没有那么积极。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他们还是去了休伊的那口井。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊把他拉上来的时候，休伊并没有马上从壳里出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们不得不轻轻敲了敲他的壳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！是你们啊！我以为你们不会再来了呢。”休伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>343692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>349444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊解释说他们前一天没有想出什么愿望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>349445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>356362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但今天我有愿望了。”鲍比满脸笑容地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>356363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>360984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望，”他用戏剧性的语调说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>360985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>368316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的镇上发生一些有趣的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>